UID:10015937-1773948600-1773959400@golocal.coop
SUMMARY:BlueByrds and Sorentinos at The California Theatre
DESCRIPTION:A joyful night of folk-rock favorites and originals with The Sorentinos & The Bluebyrds.\nThe Sorentinos team up with The Bluebyrds for a high-energy evening of beautifully crafted original songs and beloved folk/rock classics. Led by Danny Sorentino\, The Sorentinos have been wowing Bay Area audiences for over 40 years with their musicianship\, heart\, and infectious good-time spirit. Expect rich harmonies\, familiar grooves\, and plenty of reasons to get up and dance.\nThe Bluebyrds celebrate an entire era of music\, channeling the jangle and soul of folk-rock icons like The Byrds\, Buffalo Springfield\, Bob Dylan\, The Lovin’ Spoonful\, and more. This seasoned Sonoma County lineup brings the soundtrack of the ’60s—and the generations it inspired—roaring back to life. You’ll know the songs\, you’ll sing along\, and you’ll leave smiling.\nLinda Hutchinson: Bass & Vocals\nRick Minervini: Drums\nSteven Nank: Acoustic & Electric Guitars\, Harmonica & Vocals\nTom Richardson: Acoustic & Electric 6 & 12 string Guitars & Vocals \nTickets $12 in advance\, $18 at the door. Doors open 6:30pm.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/bluebyrds-and-sorentinos-at-the-california-theatre/
LOCATION:The California Theatre of Santa Rosa\, 528 7th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Bluebyrds.jpg
GEO:38.44252;-122.71621
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=The California Theatre of Santa Rosa 528 7th Street Santa Rosa CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=528 7th Street:geo:-122.71621,38.44252
END:VEVENT
