SUMMARY:The Blues Burners at The Penngrove Pub
DESCRIPTION:It’s All About The Groove \nThe BluesBurners throw down a spicy mix of funk\, rock\, electric blues\, and old school R & B. Voted favorite local band by KRSH listeners and nominated for a NORBAY for Best R&B/Blues Band\, The BluesBurners are an experienced and talented blend of musicians whose motto “It’s All About the Groove” makes our mission clear. We aim to move you\, groove you\, put a smile on your lips and make you shake your hips! \n“Lead singer KC Camarillo packs so much grit and soul into every blue note…get up and go happy go lucky blues…they’ve earned their chops and what more can I say about KC Camarillo’s dynamite pipes.” \n— John Beck
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-blues-burners-at-the-penngrove-pub/
LOCATION:Penngrove Pub\, 10005 Main Street\, Penngrove\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
