SUMMARY:Macbeth presented by Cinnabar Theater Young Rep
DESCRIPTION:A dark and thrilling tale of ambition and consequence\, Shakespeare’s Macbeth comes to life through the powerful performances of Cinnabar’s Young Rep (ages 12–18). When Macbeth receives a prophecy from mysterious forces\, he sets out on a ruthless path to claim the throne of Scotland. But each act of violence only leads to more bloodshed—and the ghosts of his crimes refuse to stay buried. Murder\, madness\, and magic collide in this gripping tragedy.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/macbeth-presented-by-cinnabar-theater/2026-03-20/
LOCATION:Cinnabar Theater\, 3333 Petaluma Blvd N\, Petaluma\, CA
