SUMMARY:The Coffis Brothers at HopMonk Sebastopol
DESCRIPTION:ABOUT: \nWith two songwriters\, six albums\, and more than a thousand shows under their belt\, The Coffis Brothers have earned their reputation as modern-day torchbearers of all-American rock & roll. It’s a sound caught halfway between amplified Americana\, acoustic folk\, roadhouse R&B\, and electrifying roots music\, crafted by a pair of California-born siblings who’ve been sharing the stage since childhood\, and the five piece band filled out by Kyle Poppen (guitar)\, Aidan Collins (bass)\, and Cory Graves (drums).
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-coffis-brothers-at-hopmonk-sebastopol/
